<ab facs="#facs_225_r3l6"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc . Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_225_r3l7"><expan>ſelıgma<ex>n</ex></expan> Juden von des <expan>vıcʒtu<ex>m</ex></expan> von <expan>Aſchaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>fleıſſıg<ex>er</ex></expan> bett </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_225_r3l8"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> geleyt bey vns <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> / vnd ſein <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Juden ſuſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_225_r3l10">niht mechtıg / Daʒ vns nıht füklıch ıſt 
<del rend="strikethrough">recht </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_225_r3l9">ſölıcher ſach </ab></add> von <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_225_line_1577133910823_1721">ʒu <expan>u<ex>er</ex>fahen</expan> <expan>auſʒʒuſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> / aber vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_225_r3l13">yngedenk ſein . Vns des Juden ʒu <expan>enteẅſʒ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd keın geleyt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_225_r3l14">bey vns ʒu <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> alſuerr wır das mıt gelimpf getun <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_225_r3l16">
<add><ab facs="#facs_225_r2l1">on geuerd </ab></add> Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
