</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_225" id="111v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hannsen von Parsperg, pfleger zu Waldek</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hanns, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>Seligma<ex>n</ex></expan> des juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Seligma<ex>n</ex></expan> juden von des
                            <expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Aschaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>fleissig<ex>er</ex></expan> bett <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> geleyt
                        bey uns <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan> und sein
                            <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> juden sust niht mechtig, daz uns niht
                        füklich ist <add>sölicher sach</add> von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wegen zu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>fahen</expan>
<expan>auszzuspreche<ex>n</ex></expan>. Aber umb
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> yngedenk
                        sein, uns des juden zu <expan>entewsz<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und kein geleyt
                        bey uns zu <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, alsverr wir das mit gelimpf getun
                                <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>on geverd</add>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ip<ex>s</ex>a</expan> die Fabiani et Sebastiani.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wernh<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von Parsperg,
                            <expan>hawbtma<ex>n</ex></expan> zu der Freyenstat, und
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Parsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Hirsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan><lb/>Cristoff von Parsperg,
                                <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> zu Hohemburg,
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
